                    <div class="mt-16 bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-lg default-shadow ">
                        <div class="mb-8">
                            <h3 class="mb-2 text-[1.35rem] md:text-[2rem] font-bold">Koľko si chcete požičať?</h3>
                            <input type="text" class="input-default"
